[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 2.1,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.72,
    "endTime": 10.48,
    "text": "Oh, my little backyard garden. It seems"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.48,
    "endTime": 13.75,
    "text": "like only yesterday that I planted you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.75,
    "endTime": 14.96,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.96,
    "endTime": 18.39,
    "text": "Well, time for your pruning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.39,
    "endTime": 21.279,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.279,
    "endTime": 25.439,
    "text": "Holy cow. How long has it been?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.439,
    "endTime": 28.48,
    "text": "Two and a half years. Well, don't worry,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.48,
    "endTime": 32.398,
    "text": "garden. I'll get you straightened out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.399,
    "endTime": 34.16,
    "text": "Shouldn't be too tough. Just got to make"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.16,
    "endTime": 35.76,
    "text": "it across the yard to the shed where I"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.76,
    "endTime": 37.92,
    "text": "keep my heavy duty gardening tools. I'll"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.92,
    "endTime": 42.44,
    "text": "have you all cleaned up in a jiffy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.28,
    "endTime": 47.039,
    "text": "Shed? Where's that shed?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.039,
    "endTime": 48.8,
    "text": "It's as if this endless tangle of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.8,
    "endTime": 52.16,
    "text": "vegetation keeps shifting, changing,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.16,
    "endTime": 56.0,
    "text": "playing tricks on my mind."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.0,
    "endTime": 60.239,
    "text": "The bones here have grown huge."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.64,
    "endTime": 62.64,
    "text": "And even the plants have developed a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.64,
    "endTime": 66.359,
    "text": "taste for flesh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.06,
    "endTime": 69.76,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.76,
    "endTime": 72.64,
    "text": "At night, it feels as if something else"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.64,
    "endTime": 76.96,
    "text": "is there. Some kind of creature watching"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.96,
    "endTime": 79.96,
    "text": "me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.56,
    "endTime": 86.08,
    "text": "Or maybe it's just my imagination."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.08,
    "endTime": 88.88,
    "text": "By day, I forage for food. Most of the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.88,
    "endTime": 92.56,
    "text": "plant life here is poisonous,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.56,
    "endTime": 95.2,
    "text": "forcing me to survive on a diet of grubs"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.2,
    "endTime": 98.52,
    "text": "and worms."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.64,
    "endTime": 102.24,
    "text": "Of course, those are poisonous, too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.24,
    "endTime": 105.68,
    "text": "Last night, it was back. The creature,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.68,
    "endTime": 108.57,
    "text": "it seems to be growing boulder."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.57,
    "endTime": 110.24,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.24,
    "endTime": 112.159,
    "text": "I fear that if I don't find that shed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.159,
    "endTime": 117.118,
    "text": "soon, this place will be the end of me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.22,
    "endTime": 123.84,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.84,
    "endTime": 126.0,
    "text": "Woo!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.0,
    "endTime": 127.24,
    "text": "Gotcha!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.24,
    "endTime": 130.979,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.08,
    "endTime": 149.789,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.29,
    "endTime": 158.79,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.79,
    "endTime": 161.599,
    "text": "[Applause]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.599,
    "endTime": 164.599,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.319,
    "endTime": 167.95,
    "text": "Pluto,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.95,
    "endTime": 169.68,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.68,
    "endTime": 171.76,
    "text": "no wonder I haven't seen you around the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.76,
    "endTime": 174.16,
    "text": "house. You've been out here in the yard"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.16,
    "endTime": 177.599,
    "text": "for several months. Apparently,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.599,
    "endTime": 179.76,
    "text": "you weren't stalking me. You were"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.76,
    "endTime": 182.159,
    "text": "protecting me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.159,
    "endTime": 186.36,
    "text": "The shed. Where?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.36,
    "endTime": 194.44,
    "text": "Come on, boy. Let's mow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.55,
    "endTime": 195.89,
    "text": "[Applause]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.89,
    "endTime": 197.12,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.12,
    "endTime": 200.72,
    "text": "A my little backyard garden. All pruned"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.72,
    "endTime": 204.0,
    "text": "and precious and back to normal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.0,
    "endTime": 205.92,
    "text": "Now, let's go hire a gardener because"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.92,
    "endTime": 210.44,
    "text": "we're never coming out here again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.84,
    "endTime": 218.99,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.99,
    "endTime": 220.21,
    "text": "[Applause]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.21,
    "endTime": 227.729,
    "text": "[Music]"
  }
]